{"tid":1133054,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"英佮扮工室XXIII","createTime":"2019-04-30T18:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T19:05:01.000Z","uid":57047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb77aff1fc5a671dfbd275cc737b0c6ae2a62d31","tid":1133054,"uid":57047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"The first step to UK is to read through all the information provided (google it yourself if necessary)<br />\nas some British might not even know how to do their job (HR are all the same around the globe)<br />\n<br />\nVisa<br />\n<br />\nTier 5 (Youth Mobility Scheme) visa - Also known as working holiday<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-5-youth-mobility&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgECUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=7274a0ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility</a><br />\n<br />\nDon't worry about below if you are using BNO<br />\nNote: If you&rsquo;re applying this visa using HKSAR passport<br />\nYou need to be sponsored<br />\nThere will be an annual quota<br />\n<br />\nTier 2 (General) visa<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-2-general&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgECUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=03b6f8b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general</a><br />\n<br />\nthis shit is such a long and painful process, especially if your employer is not familiar to this visa<br />\n<br />\nYou can apply for a Tier 2 (General) visa if:<br />\nyou&rsquo;ve been OFFERED a skilled job in the UK<br />\n<br />\nApply to settle<br />\n<br />\nIf you truly love your life in UK<br />\nyou might apply to settle<br />\n<br />\nOption 1<br />\n<br />\nIf you have been living in UK for 10 years<br />\nand met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Flong-residence%2Feligibility&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgECUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=125e2337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility</a><br />\n<br />\nOption 2<br />\nIf you have been living and working (under Tier 2) in the UK for 5 years<br />\nand met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fsettle-in-the-uk%2Fy%2Fyou-have-a-work-visa%2Ftier-2-general-visa&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgECUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=ef9178cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa</a><br />\n4<br />\n1<br />\n#2友人s&bull;1 個月前<br />\nCommon myths#1<br />\nI need English C2 level to get a job.<br />\n<br />\nNope you don't, B2 is doable.<br />\n<br />\nCommon myths #2<br />\nA smaller firm is more likely to help with visa issues.<br />\n<br />\nNo, not likely at all.<br />\n<br />\nCommon myths #3<br />\nMPH is not a urban legend"},{"pid":"de17e178f3132fa2e197561ffcfb8ccbefbb6393","tid":1133054,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:25:34.000Z","msg":"#2友人s&bull;1 個月前"},{"pid":"47c252d0ab2acce215db27cd5229ba5b5a324f67","tid":1133054,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359587334fd9daea3fb1ed4f429e6d081950922f","tid":1133054,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96671a0669f093382b77db38ad9faeeb659dbfa5","tid":1133054,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal